 108:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/portmacro.h **** 
 109:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/portmacro.h **** 	/* 32-bit tick type on a 32-bit architecture, so reads of the tick count do
 110:FreeRTOS/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/portmacro.h **** 	not need to be guarded with a critical section. */
